Class PseudoPlacement

    java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.util.EventListener, Identifiable, Definable<Placement>

    public class PseudoPlacement
extends Placement
    A PseudoPlacement is a copy of a placement or fiducial located on one of a panel's descendants that is only used for panel alignment.
